Table Commands :- 

| Command    | Use                             |
| ---------- | ------------------------------- |
| `CREATE`   | Create database/table           | # kisi bhi table ka schema decide krna/ ky columns honge use design krna
| `INSERT`   | Add records                     | # add rows/ tuples
| `SELECT`   | Read records                    |
| `UPDATE`   | Modify records                  |
| `DELETE`   | Remove records                  |
| `ALTER`    | Change table structure          |
| `DROP`     | Delete table/database           |
| `TRUNCATE` | Remove all rows, keep structure | # clear contents
| `COMMIT`   | Save changes                    |
| `ROLLBACK` | Undo uncommitted changes        |





CREATE DATABASE xyz; # yedi same name ki file exist kr rahi hogi DB main toh 'ERROR' degi, execute nahi hogi
CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS xyz;   # yedi same name ki file exist kr rahi hogi DB main toh 'Warning' degi, pr execute hogi

